text:
Infographic: Did Zuma and Parliament keep their Sona 2016 promises? 2017-02-07 11:25 
Ahead of the State of the Nation Address on Thursday, we reflect on some of the key promises that President Jacob Zuma made during his opening speech last year. 
Some of them include cost cutting measures, migration policy, healthcare improvement and higher education. Find out where the policies are a year later. Read more on:
